1
00:02:16,410 --> 00:02:18,160
Just in time.

2
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,580
Luffy...

3
00:02:22,580 --> 00:02:23,750
Pell...

4
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:27,500
There's not much time until
the square is blown up...

5
00:02:31,210 --> 00:02:32,300
Everyone...

6
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:35,050
has already fallen...

7
00:02:38,010 --> 00:02:42,770
No one can hear me anymore...

8
00:02:44,020 --> 00:02:47,150
At this rate, the country will...

9
00:02:49,940 --> 00:02:51,820
Don't worry.

10
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:58,570
We can hear your voice!

11
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:12,510
Again, I'm obviously
way more injured than you!

12
00:03:12,510 --> 00:03:17,390
Be a man and suck it up!
My leg is injured! I can't sta–

13
00:03:17,390 --> 00:03:18,800
Oh, I feel faint. This is bad...

14
00:03:19,350 --> 00:03:20,930
Yeah, right!

15
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:28,650
Be careful, Luffy.

16
00:03:29,110 --> 00:03:32,610
I ate lots of meat,
so I got lots of blood!

17
00:03:37,110 --> 00:03:38,030
I won't...

18
00:03:38,820 --> 00:03:40,910
lose again!

19
00:03:41,450 --> 00:03:45,120
How did he get out of that
quicksand with those injuries...?

20
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:53,090
Luffy's alive!

21
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,050
Tony!

22
00:03:56,050 --> 00:03:58,050
Wh-Wh-What?!

23
00:03:58,050 --> 00:03:59,470
Luffy!

24
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:01,180
Vivi's here, too!

25
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:06,560
See?! See?! I told you! I knew it!

26
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,730
Really?

27
00:04:07,730 --> 00:04:10,520
You sure don't look like
someone who knew.

28
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:14,860
Usopp! Sanji!

29
00:04:15,990 --> 00:04:17,860
What happened, my sweet Vivi?!

30
00:04:17,860 --> 00:04:19,570
You're hurt so bad!

31
00:04:20,030 --> 00:04:21,740
Usopp!

32
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:24,740
Nami... Mr. Bushido...

33
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:29,210
Everyone's okay...

34
00:04:29,210 --> 00:04:33,800
Who asked you to make
some party prop?!

35
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,880
How the hell are you standing?!

36
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:38,170
Nami my love!

37
00:04:38,170 --> 00:04:42,220
I-It had that crazy strong
attack though, right?

38
00:04:42,220 --> 00:04:45,220
I'll deal with you later!

39
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:46,060
Vivi...

40
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:50,190
What's with this sandstorm?
Do you know what's going on?

41
00:04:50,190 --> 00:04:50,940
Yes...

42
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,150
Hey, jackass!

43
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:56,150
Why is my precious Nami injured?!

44
00:04:56,150 --> 00:04:57,480
I'm gonna gut you!

45
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,900
She's just fine, isn't she...?

46
00:05:00,990 --> 00:05:03,740
Chopper, do me one last favor...

47
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:06,370
Will you please bury
my body out in the desert...?

48
00:05:06,990 --> 00:05:09,960
His wounds were fatal!

49
00:05:10,290 --> 00:05:11,870
Sorry, guys.

50
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:15,590
He beat me last time.

51
00:05:17,090 --> 00:05:18,550
But...

52
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:20,970
I won't lose again!

53
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:22,260
I'll leave the rest to you!

54
00:05:23,010 --> 00:05:24,720
Just go already.

55
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:29,350
If you can't win...

56
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:32,600
who the hell can?!

57
00:05:38,570 --> 00:05:40,070
I'm gonna put an end...

58
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:43,240
to all this!

59
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,410
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

60
00:05:50,500 --> 00:05:51,620
Everyone...

61
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,750
I'm glad I still have...

62
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,460
so many friends...

63
00:06:03,430 --> 00:06:06,680
You bastard!

64
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:19,570
Flail all you want, but you
won't be able to hit me.

65
00:06:19,980 --> 00:06:22,280
Looks like you want
to be skewered again.

66
00:06:58,980 --> 00:07:00,230
Gum-Gum...

67
00:07:00,730 --> 00:07:02,650
Who in the world is that?!

68
00:07:14,330 --> 00:07:16,670
Could he have...?!

69
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:20,250
Buzzsaw!

70
00:07:49,410 --> 00:07:51,240
He hit Crocodile...!

71
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:09,760
Well, well...

72
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,690
Get up.

73
00:08:24,530 --> 00:08:29,700
It all clicked when that water
from Yuba got on your hand...

74
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:34,080
When you get wet,
you can't turn into sand!

75
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:39,960
You stole the rain cause you're
afraid of water, didn't you?

76
00:08:43,860 --> 00:08:46,210
Now I can kick your ass.

77
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,970
The real fight starts now.

78
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,010
What?!

79
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:56,850
They're gonna bomb
the square in ten minutes?!

80
00:08:57,250 --> 00:08:58,450
Ten minutes?!

81
00:08:58,450 --> 00:09:00,100
No time to think, huh?!

82
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:03,150
But if the diameter is five kilometers,

83
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:07,610
the guy firing would have to be two
and a half kilometers from here, right?!

84
00:09:07,610 --> 00:09:09,110
No, I doubt that!

85
00:09:09,110 --> 00:09:13,030
The cannoneer is most
likely near the square!

86
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:15,200
What?! Why?!

87
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:18,200
If so, then they'd get
caught in the explosion!

88
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:21,290
That's the kind of man Crocodile is...

89
00:09:21,290 --> 00:09:23,750
He doesn't care
if his own soldiers die?!

90
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,460
What a crafty bastard...

91
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,470
Let's go already!

92
00:09:40,810 --> 00:09:43,020
We found you, Princess Vivi!

93
00:09:43,020 --> 00:09:46,650
I wonder how big of a promotion
I'll get if I kill you...

94
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:49,490
Billions!

95
00:09:49,820 --> 00:09:51,820
Ten minutes minus...
how many seconds?

96
00:09:51,820 --> 00:09:54,570
Hey, we're wasting time talking.

97
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,280
Two seconds max!

98
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,280
Two seconds max!

99
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:57,620
I'll go on ahead!

100
00:09:57,620 --> 00:09:58,740
– I'll go too!
– I'll go too!

101
00:10:02,670 --> 00:10:04,130
Don't slow down, idiot!

102
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:07,920
Let's split up! We can't do anything
until we're out of this storm!

103
00:10:11,340 --> 00:10:12,380
Ten more minutes...!

104
00:10:13,010 --> 00:10:14,510
Okay, hurry up! Let's go!

105
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:15,680
Yeah!

106
00:10:16,350 --> 00:10:19,930
This truly is... our last chance!

107
00:10:20,770 --> 00:10:22,480
The next ten minutes...

108
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:26,940
will decide this country's fate...!

109
00:10:35,570 --> 00:10:38,240
You really think you can beat me?

110
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:39,790
Yeah.

111
00:10:40,430 --> 00:10:44,460
I am impressed you figured it out,
especially so close to death...

112
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:49,500
But that's still nowhere near enough
to put you on my level—

113
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:52,720
the level of the Seven Warlords.

114
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:55,630
So what if you're one
of the Seven Warlords?

115
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:56,970
Then, that makes me...

116
00:10:57,970 --> 00:10:59,430
the eighth Warlord!

117
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:05,350
Who in the world is that man?

118
00:11:05,730 --> 00:11:06,980
He's a pirate.

119
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:09,020
Haven't you heard?

120
00:11:09,020 --> 00:11:13,650
Looks like the princess
escaped death once again.

121
00:11:13,650 --> 00:11:18,070
Then he must be the one
who brought Vivi back...

122
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:22,620
Gum-Gum...

123
00:11:22,620 --> 00:11:24,210
Pistol!

124
00:11:24,580 --> 00:11:27,460
Your strategy fails
if I just dodge your attacks.

125
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:29,250
Whether it's wet or not...

126
00:11:30,380 --> 00:11:34,050
my hand can absorb any kind of fluid.

127
00:11:34,050 --> 00:11:36,260
Sh-Shoot! I forgot he could do that!

128
00:11:49,900 --> 00:11:51,900
You said it yourself, didn't you?

129
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,490
Devil fruit abilities can be...

130
00:11:56,490 --> 00:11:58,360
as strong as any weapon.

131
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,280
It just depends on how you use it.

132
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:03,370
Gum-Gum Pistol!

133
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,210
Shotgun!

134
00:12:11,210 --> 00:12:12,670
Impudent brat!

135
00:12:12,670 --> 00:12:14,340
Desert Spada!

136
00:12:15,460 --> 00:12:16,380
That thing again?!

137
00:12:22,220 --> 00:12:23,810
That was close...

138
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:26,430
Gum-Gum...!

139
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:30,350
The same technique
over and over again...

140
00:12:30,350 --> 00:12:31,690
Are you even trying to win?

141
00:12:31,690 --> 00:12:32,400
Yeah!

142
00:12:33,070 --> 00:12:34,070
I sure am!

143
00:12:37,490 --> 00:12:39,780
This was my goal from the start!

144
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:41,070
Time to get soaked!

145
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:43,200
I saw that coming from a mile away!

146
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:45,200
Sables!

147
00:12:55,630 --> 00:12:57,590
Come back, barrel!

148
00:13:01,890 --> 00:13:04,390
You're struggling desperately,
Straw Hat Luffy...

149
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:08,060
See, you've become
too reliant on that barrel.

150
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:10,980
This isn't any different
from our first fight.

151
00:13:13,940 --> 00:13:15,940
You're right.

152
00:13:16,650 --> 00:13:18,860
Nothing's changed yet.

153
00:13:27,700 --> 00:13:28,950
Well, how about this?!

154
00:13:30,540 --> 00:13:32,540
I'm way different now.

155
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:34,590
Are you serious?

156
00:13:37,210 --> 00:13:38,710
Water Luffy!

157
00:13:39,740 --> 00:13:41,680
Oh no! This is bad! I sprung a leak!

158
00:13:42,220 --> 00:13:43,930
Is this brat...

159
00:13:43,930 --> 00:13:45,680
messing with me...?

160
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:48,770
Belly's sloshing around...

161
00:13:51,310 --> 00:13:53,350
I guess I drank too much...

162
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:58,280
Does he not understand
the gravity of the situation?

163
00:14:06,990 --> 00:14:09,950
Stop playing around, you damn brat!

164
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,010
Dammit!

165
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:27,680
Who's playing around?!

166
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:29,350
My body...

167
00:14:30,140 --> 00:14:32,890
I'm always serious!

168
00:14:32,890 --> 00:14:34,350
Gum-Gum...

169
00:14:36,810 --> 00:14:38,520
Bazooka!

170
00:14:59,460 --> 00:15:02,170
How's that... sandodile?!

171
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:07,930
I can't believe it...!

172
00:15:07,930 --> 00:15:09,930
Crocodile was actually beaten...?

173
00:15:10,430 --> 00:15:13,890
This is no time to be
impressed, right, Mr. Cobra?

174
00:15:17,770 --> 00:15:20,940
Now, you're going to take me...

175
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:23,490
to the poneglyph!

176
00:15:25,030 --> 00:15:29,030
Why do you want to see
something like that?

177
00:15:32,540 --> 00:15:34,410
Don't ask pointless questions.

178
00:15:34,410 --> 00:15:37,250
All you have to do is lead the way.

179
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:46,970
I wonder if your luck is running out...

180
00:15:46,970 --> 00:15:48,430
There isn't much time left.

181
00:15:53,180 --> 00:15:55,810
Go already, Nico Robin...

182
00:15:55,810 --> 00:15:58,400
unless you wish
to wither away as well.

183
00:15:59,020 --> 00:16:02,860
My patience... is running thin...

184
00:16:03,230 --> 00:16:05,070
Nico Robin?!

185
00:16:05,740 --> 00:16:07,780
Very well. As you wish.

186
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:12,240
Listen carefully, Straw Hat.

187
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:15,040
Even the rock in this courtyard...

188
00:16:15,040 --> 00:16:16,960
can wither away.

189
00:16:25,460 --> 00:16:27,510
The grass is drying up!

190
00:16:32,930 --> 00:16:34,810
Ground Secco!

191
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:39,850
What the heck...?!

192
00:16:42,270 --> 00:16:44,070
I'm falling!

193
00:16:45,070 --> 00:16:46,780
Th-That was close!

194
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:48,780
That big jerk!

195
00:16:48,780 --> 00:16:51,620
Water-Water Pistol!

196
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:57,580
What?! He swallowed it with his hand!

197
00:16:57,970 --> 00:17:02,500
You thought you nullified
my powers, "Water Luffy"...?

198
00:17:04,380 --> 00:17:07,460
That was a grave mistake.

199
00:17:08,010 --> 00:17:11,260
The true power of sand
is dehydration.

200
00:17:11,260 --> 00:17:12,470
Behold.

201
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:17,680
My right hand dries out everything...

202
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:20,690
There's no limit to its power.

203
00:17:46,630 --> 00:17:48,170
The rock...

204
00:17:48,170 --> 00:17:50,130
Even statues are turning into sand...

205
00:17:54,010 --> 00:17:55,510
The ground...

206
00:17:55,510 --> 00:17:57,010
is dying...!

207
00:17:58,430 --> 00:17:59,470
Even my sandles!

208
00:18:00,230 --> 00:18:03,100
Everything connected to this hand...

209
00:18:03,730 --> 00:18:05,650
will shrivel up and die!

210
00:18:05,730 --> 00:18:08,070
Ground Death!

211
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:33,630
You picked a perfect time
to show up, Marines.

212
00:18:33,630 --> 00:18:36,090
Out of the way. We're in a hurry.

213
00:18:36,090 --> 00:18:37,510
I'm afraid we can't!

214
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:42,100
I heard the situation from
a soldier here in Alubarna.

215
00:18:42,850 --> 00:18:46,480
Who do you think that person is?!

216
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:48,730
Well, I don't care who he is.

217
00:18:48,730 --> 00:18:51,440
I hate people in the government.

218
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:54,570
If you don't get out of my way...

219
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:57,570
We have no intention
of letting you pass!

220
00:18:58,580 --> 00:19:00,740
Then I'll simply kill you.

221
00:19:00,740 --> 00:19:03,410
Wait, Marines! Don't worry about me!

222
00:19:03,410 --> 00:19:05,710
We were told a cannon
will be fired at 4:30

223
00:19:05,710 --> 00:19:09,170
right into the palace square
where the rebellion is happening!

224
00:19:09,170 --> 00:19:11,510
Please, you must
find a way to stop it!

225
00:19:11,510 --> 00:19:12,800
What...?!

226
00:19:13,800 --> 00:19:14,970
Only seven minutes...!

227
00:19:15,340 --> 00:19:18,720
A million citizens' lives are at stake!

228
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,680
Even so...

229
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:23,890
We'll save you,
then stop the explosion!

230
00:19:23,890 --> 00:19:25,270
Wait! This woman is–

231
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:26,850
Ready!

232
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,770
Don't get in my way!

233
00:19:29,150 --> 00:19:30,690
Treinta Fleurs!

234
00:19:31,940 --> 00:19:33,190
Strangle!

235
00:19:34,780 --> 00:19:35,650
A devil fruit...!

236
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:37,780
I said I was in a hurry, didn't I?!

237
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:39,870
Don't make me upset!

238
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:42,950
Sergeant Major!

239
00:19:42,950 --> 00:19:44,790
This woman is Nico Robin!

240
00:19:45,710 --> 00:19:46,830
I'm sure of it!

241
00:19:47,330 --> 00:19:51,090
Per Captain Smoker's orders,
I looked for her wanted poster.

242
00:19:51,090 --> 00:19:53,090
She has a bounty on her head!

243
00:19:53,090 --> 00:19:57,180
She was known all over
the world twenty years ago!

244
00:19:57,180 --> 00:20:01,100
I remember reading about it
in the papers at the time.

245
00:20:01,100 --> 00:20:05,350
There was an incident where
six Marine warships were sunk.

246
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:09,810
They said it was the work
of a single eight-year-old girl!

247
00:20:09,810 --> 00:20:13,940
The government declared
her a significant risk,

248
00:20:13,940 --> 00:20:18,070
and the bounty given was
a whopping 79 million belly!

249
00:20:18,070 --> 00:20:22,120
However, she suddenly
disappeared after that.

250
00:20:22,120 --> 00:20:23,870
Stop your rambling!

251
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:26,960
Will you clear the way,
or will you die?! Which is it?!

252
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:30,250
Numbers don't matter against her...

253
00:20:33,170 --> 00:20:36,670
Sergeant! Take everyone to
the square and stop the explosion!

254
00:20:36,670 --> 00:20:37,880
But, Sergeant Major...!

255
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:40,260
Hurry! There're only six minutes left!

256
00:20:40,260 --> 00:20:41,180
Yes, ma'am!

257
00:20:47,930 --> 00:20:50,560
Now, let that man go!

258
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:52,810
I told you not to get in my way!

259
00:21:27,770 --> 00:21:29,600
That was close!

260
00:21:29,600 --> 00:21:31,900
His right hand is a real problem...

261
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:36,270
The lawn turned into a desert!

262
00:21:38,860 --> 00:21:40,860
Where'd he go?

263
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:51,500
You made me waste my energy...

264
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:02,880
You missed...

265
00:22:05,100 --> 00:22:06,810
Croco...

266
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:22,150
Once again...

267
00:22:22,150 --> 00:22:24,110
you lose...

268
00:22:25,320 --> 00:22:27,370
Straw Hat Luffy.

